name: Anesthesia 2021
content: The 6th edition of the International Conference on Anesthesia will be organized in Rome, Italy, September 20-21, 2021 following the successful previous editions of Valencia 2019, Dublin 2018, London 2017, and San Antonio 2016\. Anesthesia 2021 which aims to gather the most elegant societies and industries along with the renowned and honorable persons form top universities across the globe. Anesthesia 2021 on behalf of its organizing Committee welcomes all the Anesthesia researchers, industrialists, doctors, young scientists as well as student and corporate delegates to participate and to have a great experience.
